About this item

  • Features: The womens bow sweater features a classic crew neck and short sleeves, striped pattern, crochet hollow out design, the bow tie front closure allow for easy layering and a customizable fit, making it a staple for your daily wardrobe.
  • Material: This tie front cropped sweater is made of soft, lightweight and skin-friendly fabric, the crochet hollowed-out design creates a casual and feminine look perfect for any occasion.
  • Mathing: This beach sweaters for women can be styled as a tops or a shrug, pairing with camisoles, dresses, sleeveless outfits, shorts, jeans, skirts, leggings, trousers for a trendy weekend outfit. Or layer it as a cover-up for a swimsuit at the beach or pool.
  • Occasions: This summer tops is suitable for a variety of settings from vacation to daily wear, like beach, casual, vacation, going out, school, party, dating, holiday, date night, and daily wear in spring and summer, making you look different and chic.
  • Size: Size Small fits size 4 - size 6, size Medium fits size 8 - size 10, size Large fits size 12 - size 14, size X-Large fits size 16, size XX-Large fits size 18. More specific information about this tie front tops for women please refer to the size chart we provided in the pictures.

    I picked this up for my wife as a surprise and she was a bit apprehensive about it. But she usually pairs it with a cami and jeans it looks good. She wore it while traveling across the country and reported that it was comfortable and unobtrusive. I got her the green apricot stripe, and that color really compliments her eyes (they are green). She is 5'9", 38 bust and the Large fits her well.
    The crochet holes are big enough that you wouldn't want to wear this without some sort of top (unless you're the more 'adventurous' type). As a swimsuit coverup, you'd have to have a separate skirt or something as this is not long enough to cover your entire torso.
    The construction seems to be a good quality...she didn't notice any stray strings or any seems that seem weak. Being crocheted, I would imagine that it is a more delicate item.
